overview: AccuteX EDM is the exclusive U.S. importer for Taiwanese EDM machine manufacturer AccuteX Technologies. We offer a wide range of CNC Wire EDMs, Small Hole EDMs, and Die Sinkers across the United States and Canada. Our mission is to provide high-quality, user-friendly and economical products from the best machine manufacturers. Our products deliver accuracy, reliability and cutting-edge performance, and are committed to providing advanced solutions and training services to EDM machine suppliers.
